[test gen_read.it]
# gen47: the induced generative loop is language-neutral BY CONSTRUCTION.
# gen41 made `read:` induce the continuation model from the read prose itself;
# nothing in it is English-specific, so reading Italian prose induces an Italian
# model and `say` speaks Italian -- with zero language-specific code. This is the
# deep point of the probe: the *induced* half was multilingual all along; only
# the hand-written parsers needed the canonicalization layer.
> read: il gatto dorme sul divano. il gatto dorme spesso.
< Learned 0 fact(s), skipped 2.
# Generation reflects the read Italian text, frequency-then-order ranked.
> say il
< the
> say gatto
< cat
> say dorme
< sleep
